==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stinkwood
<hw>Stink"wood`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A name given to several kinds of wood with an unpleasant smell, as
that of the <spn>Foetidia Mauritiana</spn> of the Mauritius, and that of
the South African <spn>Ocotea bullata</spn>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

